        },
        {
            "id": 1,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "Extracting opinion targets and opinion words from online reviews are two fundamental tasks in opinion mining . <S>\r",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 2,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "This paper proposes a novel approach \r",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 3,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "to collectively extract them with graph co-ranking . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "First , compared to previous methods \r",
            "relation": "COMPARISON"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "which solely employed opinion relations among words , \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "our method constructs a heterogeneous graph \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "to model two types of relations , \r",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "including semantic relations and opinion relations . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "Next , a co-ranking algorithm is proposed \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "to estimate the confidence of each candidate , \r",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 10,
            "text": "and the candidates with higher confidence will be extracted as opinion targets/words . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "In this way , different relations make cooperative effects on candidate's confidence estimation . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "Moreover , word preference is captured and incorporated into our co-ranking algorithm . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "In this way , our co-ranking is personalized \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "parent": 14,
            "text": "and each candidate's confidence is only determined by its preferred collocations . <S>\r",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 16,
            "parent": 13,
            "text": "It helps to improve the extraction precision . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 17,
            "parent": 18,
            "text": "The experimental results on three data sets with different sizes and languages show \r",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 18,
            "parent": 2,
            "text": "that our approach achieves better performance than state-of-the-art methods . <S>\r",
            "relation": "EVALUATION"
        }
    ]
}